txt.en: A number of cruel crebain have settled in alongside the Tarkrîp Orcs, waiting to feast upon the corpses of Men when the Orcs have had their say.\n\nThese merciless birds should be driven off, for they fill you with an unpleasant sense of foreboding.
You have defeated a number of the invading crebain.
